    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ strange won-der! O__ dread mys-ter--y! He that by__ na--ture__ as__ God is__ im-mor---tal and__ can-not__ die,__ how is He__ hanged on a tree; can it be He doth__ taste___ of____ death? Is He__ con-demned, Who of__ all__ is in--no---cent? Be-hold, O Sun, hide thy__ light and quake__ with___ fear at___ this__ au--dac-i---ty! Thus the Vir-gin spake with__ groans as she be-held____ hang-ing on the Cross the Sav--iour Christ,__ Whom she__ had__ borne."
    }
  }
